"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"## My search for an acre of escape\\n\\n[![Paul Greenberg](https://miro.medium.com/fit/c/56/56/1\\\\*tPfbBeQ23qMKUptWlw1FaQ.jpeg)](https://4fishgreenberg.medium.com/?source=post_page-----82252fbaae82-----------------------------------)\\n\\n![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*lvzvn8HdxUe8BXEsPxlZ5w.png)\\n\\n“Granite erratic, Dudmaston” by Richard Webb is licensed under CC BY-SA 2.0. To view a copy of this license, visit <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/2.0/?ref=openverse&atype=rich>\\n\\nIt was the rock that caught my eye. Dappled with lichen and lighted by the afternoon sun, it appeared to be the perfect place for contemplation. A spot where you could sit and write your novel, ponder your place in the universe, and perhaps reach some kind of equilibrium with the planet.\\n\",\"timestamp\":1642258579,\"title\":\"Is Anywhere Safe from Climate Change? - Paul Greenberg - Medium\"},\"digest\":\"DYcb9Ga_hUBgbGATItYJwy_MJeNaTD77S7-bZfToKYM\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x045802cC55Ab52FA57bA5F2797b5906eD98c03b4\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SyApH_1EiMXnizH77_OcWRb90rOBXaz0foh3m9WZy04\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zI6W0VtCWjwxSr2VKvNC62BJcgAFqbjBaxN-QvGM_gU\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"UeNeNpZfgCGpk-0sb9EiidC3Dc3fJwWNg6jL2KP8OUlf0ymIKIG38-RYTr1mQzVbylJjxIG7ATRMiuuj1Rn0WQ\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x9a8787096fa77d838722c55a783f31b6f33f2a9e3b81e68f7185167e25f34c1a16361eef01acba78abd0b393c4fe41f1abca60b63fd0f52273ef70a15b2428da1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"SyApH_1EiMXnizH77_OcWRb90rOBXaz0foh3m9WZy04\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"zI6W0VtCWjwxSr2VKvNC62BJcgAFqbjBaxN-QvGM_gU\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"origi